    • incrementIndexByBase

      protected Object incrementIndexByBase(Object index)
      If the index being loaded by for a List and the mapping specified a base-index, this will return the passed index value incremented by the base. Otherwise, the passed index is returned.
      Parameters:
      index - The relational index value; specifically without any mapped base applied
      Returns:
      The appropriately incremented base
